Hamish Linklater https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hamish_Linklater 0 Hamish Linklater is an American actor and playwright, known for playing Matthew Kimble in The New Adventures of Old Christine and Andrew Keanelly in The Crazy Ones. He is the son of dramatic vocal trainer Kristin Linklater.
